  "title": "Delivery Driver #78777",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Food Manufacturer</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Delivery Driver</strong></li><li>Working Location: West</li><li>Working Hours: 5-5.5 days (Mon-Fri: 8.30am-6pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Gross up to $3,000</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Loading, unloading, transportations & delivery items to clients or business in a safe & timely manner</li><li>Collect and verify delivery instructions</li><li>Adhere to safety requirement while on the job</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Skills: class 3 or class 4 driving license</li><li>Able to drive commercial vehicle</li><li>Compliant with warehouse & safety regulations</li><li>Saturday hours are treated and paid as overtime.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#78777 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
